textBox.richText: There was some confusion with the piles of handouts. You should have 36 abstracts. I will bring leftovers on Wednesday. The goal of the exercise is to read all of the abstract and classify them by attaching some of the following keywords “testing”, “modeling”, “verification”, “process”, “specification”, “languages”. The exact meaning of the terms is left to your interpretation. If you find additional keywords, feel free to add them to the list.
